title: 服务器有问题
author: john180
txt_content:
按教程弄好就跳出来这几个字
[INFO] Starting minecraft server version Beta 1.3
[INFO] Loading properties
[INFO] Starting Minecraft server on 61.171.13.200:25564
[WARNING] **** FAILED TO BIND TO PORT!
[WARNING] The exception was: java.net.BindException: Cannot assign requested address: JVM_Bind
[WARNING] Perhaps a server is already running on that port?

怎么回事啊

replies.txt_content:
回复 ffbfqqo 的帖子

重启过不知道多少次了

replies.author: liu33960
replies.txt_content:
游戏用到25565端口
这个提示 应该是有某个程序占用了这个端口 最大的可能是运行的有服务端程序（任何版本都是25565端口） 如果表面看不出来 运行“进程管理器”或者360类的工具查看一下

replies.author: john180
replies.txt_content:
回复 liu33960 的帖子

找不到有任何程序占了这个端口啊

replies.author: liu33960
replies.txt_content: 终极解决大法， 重新做系统，做好了 什么都不装 先装服务端

replies.author: john180
replies.txt_content:

换端口
